- Everything must be writen in english.
- Compile using: `cargo build --release`, unless instructed otherwise.
- Check for issues using: cargo clippy.
- #[allow(dead_code)] directive is generally forbidden to fix warnings except to silence warnings related to tests.
- Regularly check unit tests when adding, modifying or removing features.
- When a test breaks, be careful, you must check first if it's the modification the problem before adapting the test to the new change.
- Always finish by building the app and run unit tests.